  planner_response {
    modified_response: "I have successfully completed the high-fidelity React implementation of the **Logic Engine Admin Console** dashboard, delivering a clean, production-ready, and highly interactive multi-screen application styled with meticulous institutional precision.\n\n### **Design Concept & Visual Identity**\n- **Institutional Precision Theme**: Leveraged a clean, high-contrast off-white and charcoal gray aesthetic paired with sophisticated primary accent hues. The interface centers around balanced margins, structured divider borders, and generous negative space to present a complex administrative utility naturally.\n- **Advanced Micro-Interactions**: Integrated smooth transitions, active status indicators, floating alert notifications, and customized responsive form inputs to provide a polished, tactile user experience.\n- **Aesthetic Typography**: Styled display elements using clean, modern sans-serif headings paired with precise monospace families for formulas, database keys, parameters, and debug outputs.\n\n---\n\n### **Core Screens & Functional Modules**\n\n1. **Decision Tables (Spreadsheet Editor)**:\n   - Displays a high-density, real-time spreadsheet grid featuring precise fraud detection rules.\n   - Fully interactive cell modification: inline input fields, dropdown selections, active cell focus highlighting, and a dynamic country tag creator.\n   - Actionable operation commands: multi-row checkbox selection, instant rule insertion/deletion, and page navigation.\n\n2. **Rule Designer (Visual Logic Blocks)**:\n   - Implements a visual code-block builder matching the recursive logic conditions exactly (`IF`, `AND`, `OR` groups).\n   - Features beautiful nested logic indent outlines with custom sidebars, custom list tokens, toggle status behaviors, and an execution action footer.\n   - Includes a floating **Data Explorer** panel with structured tree hierarchies for data entities, enabling rapid exploration of parameters and types.\n\n3. **Rule Orchestrator (DAG Canvas)**:\n   - A fully styled, responsive layout for visual node workflows (Start Node, Data Lookup, Decision Splits, Routing Actions) connected by real SVG curves with animated running dash paths.\n   - Features a floating canvas toolbar (zoom controllers, fit-screen) and an **Interactive Property Inspector** that updates fields in real-time when any canvas node is selected.\n   - Houses an integrated **Test Scenario Runner** console with alternate testing scenarios and an automated monospace log execution tracer.\n\n4. **Detailed Configuration (Metadata Grid)**:\n   - A modern, structured card-based panel detailing administrative attributes (technical IDs, ownership parameters, descriptions).\n   - Includes custom controls for cache lifetimes, execution switches, live lifecycle options, system tag editors, and external compliance action lists.\n\n5. **Data Schema & Mathematical Functions**:\n   - Includes a schema declaration console for defining attributes, binding types (`str`, `num`, `int`, `bool`), and associating entity contexts.\n   - A dedicated directory for analytical helper formulas (`vel(24h)`, `avgSpend(30d)`) equipped with parameter definitions and an execution sandbox console.\n\n6. **Execution History logs**:\n   - Displays real-time debugging streams tracking execution latency, status outcomes (Error, Warning, Success), and timestamps.\n   - Expandable drill-down panels reveal custom-compiled timelines, structured raw inputs, and detailed error trace dumps."
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
